{"tid":204914,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人屋企人成日嗌交","createTime":"2017-04-17T11:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T16:15:16.000Z","uid":78004,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9b5fe4bf649eaa5a4646eb2879ec3ed61da2190","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:49:21.000Z","msg":"我唔想老豆老母再嘈交 呢個問題纏繞左我屋企好耐 希望大家可以有心機睇落去 比少少建議我可以點做<br />\n<br />\n講番少少背景 我呀爸番工早出門 黃昏就番黎 基本上係呀爸擔起全個屋企 我有個家姐 佢好少理屋企既野 朝早番工又好夜先番 基本上家姐自給自足 話就話唔洗養佢 不過仲要養我同媽咪 雖然我讀緊大學 但係屋企人唔想我番part time 所以會比零用錢我<br />\n<br />\n媽咪係長期病患者 佢一直都好多病纏身 糖尿病 膽固醇高 高血壓 不過我媽咪有藥物敏感 基本上係食唔到西藥 所以呢啲病無藥物比佢控制到 都係靠飲食同運動 而且佢身體好弱 聽講係以前坐月既時候無補身 所以而家成日會頭暈 係無原因既頭暈 不過間中會飲中藥調理下 正正因為佢身體比其他人弱 百病纏身 而且係長期病患者 所以個人成日都好唔開心 成日無端端喊 佢好擔心自己既病 因為藥物控制唔到 一唔舒服頭暈既時候就好想有人係佢身邊陪佢 不過屋企人個個都要番工番學 跟本無人有時間全日陪佢<br />\n<br />\n到左我地放學放工 有時都會傾下計 開解下佢 不過我老豆放左工既時候真係好攰好攰 未有太多精神擺落佢到 去陪佢傾計 病又陪實佢咁<br />\n<br />\n正正因為咁 佢地成日會因為咁樣而嘈交 我媽咪無時無刻都想人陪佢 照顧佢 而爸爸放左工只係想靜靜地抖下過一日 而唔想聽到自己老婆又講自己邊到唔舒服 近呢幾年我已經好努力 好想取代到我老豆既位置 意思係由我陪媽咪傾計 照顧佢既病 希望令佢覺得有人陪佢 明白佢 但係無論我做幾多野 佢地都會因為好微少既事而嘈起交黎 而且我有少少覺得媽咪佢有情緒病 情緒好唔穩定 無論係好小事都會好緊張 媽咪既態度一直係因為自己老公擺落佢到既精神唔夠多而發哂脾氣 而爸爸既態度就係我番工已經好攰點解仲要事事都要搵交嗌<br />\n<br />\n其實仲有一件事係令佢地經常鬧交 有次試過因爲爸爸貪玩 上網識左個大陸妹 不過純粹係網上面傾計 無出黎見過 亦都無比過錢佢話包二奶個啲 媽咪知道佢偷偷地咁做之後鬧過離婚 最後爸爸都應承會改 最後都無再發生 不過呢件事令媽咪晚影響好深好深 成日諗起呢件事就喊 一鬧交就會再提番起件事 呢件事亦都令媽咪對佢失信心 因為係媽咪心目中咁樣同包二奶無分別 佢覺得因為自己病所以去包二奶搵女人傾計 而家無論爸爸做啲乜 都會覺得唔會再相信佢 例如話佢番工係去搵女人之類 經常將呢件事放大再放大<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個鬧交既導火線令到近呢五六年 三日唔埋兩日就會嗌交 近呢五六年我亦都好大好大壓力 我好愛呢個家 唔想屋企成日都嘈 所以每次都會夾係中間做磨心 每次嘈得激烈 媽咪就會話想自殺 我已經覺得好攰 老實說講我唔怕佢地離婚 只係唔想聽到佢地係到嘈交<br />\n<br />\n講到呢到 可能有啲1999 我將自己屋企既家事講出黎 因為我已經一個人承受唔住 我都覺得好攰好攰"},{"pid":"58bc108467c3ce0ec5fe3e25c395aa6b6d978fae","tid":204914,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:51:48.000Z","msg":"Tldr"},{"pid":"a22eeca3cdb99988a543690242690873e3056fe1","tid":204914,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:53:19.000Z","msg":"再搞落去你老母真係遲早自殺&hellip;"},{"pid":"a48108c5395bd51275d2c2c15e2da08281295b5b","tid":204914,"uid":70760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:54:16.000Z","msg":"幫唔到d咩 推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55757861b2dc5e14b3e5460cc675153b890f63c9","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:54:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Tldr</blockquote><br />\n對唔住因爲件事真係太長"},{"pid":"cd0f1954bc47acec8361cdbae8805743639256d7","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:55:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再搞落去你老母真係遲早自殺&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n我都好擔心 基本上我每一日都好擔心佢地會嘈交 有時仲會偷偷地喊"},{"pid":"30f6b9b943522ce1fc6f051491d15e424f2fc64b","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫唔到d咩 推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝你"},{"pid":"db0f03b467161969cf8d1a61414e57fc32768cde","tid":204914,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:56:07.000Z","msg":"哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧願上網同第二個女人傾都唔同自己老婆傾，比著我都嬲"},{"pid":"3a26a960fb9d1a10c5b83e3f6079d50564dd66ce","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:56:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧願上網同第二個女人傾都唔同自己老婆傾，比著我都嬲</blockquote><br />\n佢自己都知道錯 不過件事真係影響媽咪好深好深"},{"pid":"ebf1aa480937cd565bbf4cab19adfdd3201779a2","tid":204914,"uid":75394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:58:20.000Z","msg":"你老母本身有冇朋友？<br />\n有d師奶friend吹吓水就一日好過1個人係屋企亂諗嘢"},{"pid":"2ea3a3ee7f34a2f3caaa43d0318e1bda5fc09e46","tid":204914,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:58:57.000Z","msg":"靠你啦 開解下阿媽 嘗試解釋下俾阿爸知情況<br />\n<br />\n自己都要識得諗 加油"},{"pid":"0a26408ed156178024610b48d0038f515b28ec64","tid":204914,"uid":78504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T11:59:14.000Z","msg":"咁又唔怪得你老豆，佢辛苦咗一日，返到屋企仲要聽你媽媽放負，俾我都頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4f96263a622e2f29512881c94a78c3c255c36aa","tid":204914,"uid":71034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧願上網同第二個女人傾都唔同自己老婆傾，比著我都嬲</blockquote><br />\n佢自己都知道錯 不過件事真係影響媽咪好深好深</blockquote><br />\n其實咁搞法你老豆遲早都會頂唔順"},{"pid":"015507eef34d05c43ac046b7d15c769279456366","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老母本身有冇朋友？<br />\n有d師奶friend吹吓水就一日好過1個人係屋企亂諗嘢</blockquote><br />\n無 佢基本上無朋友 一黎因爲無番工 無同人接觸 二黎佢好難同人相處"},{"pid":"93fabb6426948022f4ade5ff07aac5b1d748790c","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靠你啦 開解下阿媽 嘗試解釋下俾阿爸知情況<br />\n<br />\n自己都要識得諗 加油</blockquote><br />\n我已經好盡力 不過多謝你 我會再繼續試下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1d2d77cfa60931d84652bfc3bdbb06eece3edf","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁又唔怪得你老豆，佢辛苦咗一日，返到屋企仲要聽你媽媽放負，俾我都頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係係媽咪既處境係 自己病就應該要得到老公既關心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f55246faedc084a7afc816e9cbbcbca84b63fcc","tid":204914,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你老母本身有冇朋友？<br />\n有d師奶friend吹吓水就一日好過1個人係屋企亂諗嘢</blockquote><br />\n無 佢基本上無朋友 一黎因爲無番工 無同人接觸 二黎佢好難同人相處</blockquote><br />\n點解難同人相處先"},{"pid":"d92c3ffcf1624d7ae8eec09c0e16f81863dbe884","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>哇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧願上網同第二個女人傾都唔同自己老婆傾，比著我都嬲</blockquote><br />\n佢自己都知道錯 不過件事真係影響媽咪好深好深</blockquote><br />\n其實咁搞法你老豆遲早都會頂唔順</blockquote><br />\n基本上佢而家既態度已經差過以前 以前佢會哄番個老婆 而家會選擇唔理 格幾日先會再哄下"},{"pid":"903594e10af53645973ccb25e6d889e9e3032127","tid":204914,"uid":42985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"有時煩屋企野都好精神折磨"},{"pid":"3dd03d28a4786551070861373c5bc2e5231b8aa5","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:06:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你老母本身有冇朋友？<br />\n有d師奶friend吹吓水就一日好過1個人係屋企亂諗嘢</blockquote><br />\n無 佢基本上無朋友 一黎因爲無番工 無同人接觸 二黎佢好難同人相處</blockquote><br />\n點解難同人相處先</blockquote><br />\n佢性格其實幾孤辟 唔係同個個夾得黎 而且我提過覺得佢有情緒病 所以佢都幾拒絕去識朋友"},{"pid":"c0eeed06a0d95de0a846848e9f9acdab37208bea","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時煩屋企野都好精神折磨</blockquote><br />\n無錯 我已經好努力 平時要兼顧讀書 仲要兼顧埋佢地嗌交 我真係覺得好攰好辛苦"},{"pid":"9ba1aa713e1c9b4a81cea939225fdae7aaeb853c","tid":204914,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:08:22.000Z","msg":"其實到最後一係你老豆都有情緒病/ 頂唔順走佬，  一係你老母&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過拎綜援+grant loan"},{"pid":"b416102ca7ab93a7de399ed090210a1d66779474","tid":204914,"uid":22325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:09:07.000Z","msg":"如果老母入手解決唔到，就試下老豆入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終一家人，其實老母可能想要既係交流。<br />\n就算老豆番屋企放公司負都可能ok"},{"pid":"5fc995d2e4bd6db0c9d9a5b7890b7e6866138d5d","tid":204914,"uid":78004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實到最後一係你老豆都有情緒病/ 頂唔順走佬，  一係你老母&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過拎綜援+grant loan</blockquote><br />\n有 我有申請grant loan而且批full grant 但綜緩就無<br />\n不過媽咪好多病 成日要比錢睇醫生 所以爸爸都要好努力